### 8. Configuration Files

**Dockerfile:** `/Users/jim/Property/1121-Citrus-Avenue/1121-citrus/pfsense-backup/Dockerfile` (85 lines)
- Alpine 3.21 base
- Installs compression, SSH, AWS CLI, GPG tools
- Copies 4 scripts: `startup`, `backup`, `common-functions`, `healthcheck`, `pfsense-backup`
- HEALTHCHECK directive: 30-second interval, 3-second timeout
