**Trivy Ignore:** `/Users/jim/Property/1121-Citrus-Avenue/1121-citrus/pfsense-backup/.trivyignore.yaml`
- 4 CVEs ignored with justifications (urllib3 decompression bombs, cryptography ECDSA)
- Expires 2027-06-17

**Dive CI Config:** `/Users/jim/Property/1121-Citrus-Avenue/1121-citrus/pfsense-backup/.dive-ci`
- `lowestEfficiency: 0.9` (kept at default)
- `highestWastedBytes: disabled` (Alpine upgrade waste)
- `highestUserWastedPercent: 0.20` (relaxed from 0.10 for apk upgrade)

**Dependabot:** `/Users/jim/Property/1121-Citrus-Avenue/1121-citrus/pfsense-backup/.github/dependabot.yml`
- GitHub Actions updates: weekly on Mondays at 06:00 UTC
- Labels: `dependencies`, `github-actions`

**Markdown Lint:** `/Users/jim/Property/1121-Citrus-Avenue/1121-citrus/pfsense-backup/.markdownlint.json`
- Disables 10 rules for flexibility with markdown style

**Docker Ignore:** `/Users/jim/Property/1121-Citrus-Avenue/1121-citrus/pfsense-backup/.dockerignore`
